<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Symbol on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/symbol/</link><description>Recent content in Symbol on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/symbol/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Kotlin Unresolved Reference — Name Not Found Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/unresolved-reference/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/unresolved-reference/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="unresolved-reference--name-not-found-fix"&gt;Unresolved Reference — Name Not Found Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An unresolved reference error occurs at compile time when Kotlin cannot find the referenced variable, function, class, or property. This is one of the most common compile errors in Kotlin.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kotlin must be able to resolve every name you use to a declared symbol. If the name doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist, isn&amp;rsquo;t imported, or isn&amp;rsquo;t visible, the compiler reports an unresolved reference error.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Undefined symbol</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/assembly/undefined-symbol/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/assembly/undefined-symbol/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An undefined symbol error occurs when the assembler or linker encounters a reference to a label, function, or variable that has not been defined anywhere in the source files or linked libraries. This is a link-time error that prevents the executable from being produced.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing &lt;code&gt;global&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;extern&lt;/code&gt; declaration for a symbol&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typo in a function or variable name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forgetting to link against the library that provides the symbol&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Referencing a label that was removed or renamed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-asm" data-lang="asm"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; WRONG: Using a symbol without declaring it
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;section&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;.text&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;call&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my_function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; where is my_function defined?
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; CORRECT: Declare external symbols or define them
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;extern&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my_function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; declared in another object file
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;section&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;.text&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;call&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;my_function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; linker will resolve this
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-asm" data-lang="asm"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; WRONG: Forgetting to export a symbol for other files
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;section&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;.text&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;helper_func:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;mov&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;rax&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ret&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; CORRECT: Mark the symbol as global so other files can use it
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;section&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;.text&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;global&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;helper_func&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;helper_func:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;mov&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;rax&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ret&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-asm" data-lang="asm"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;section&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;.text&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;global&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_start&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;_start:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;call&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;calculate&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; undefined - never defined anywhere
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;mov&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;rdi&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;rax&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;mov&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;rax&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;60&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;syscall&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; Symbol is missing entirely - linker will fail:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;; ld: undefined symbol: calculate
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/assembly/linker-error"&gt;Linker error: undefined reference&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/assembly/invalid-instruction"&gt;Invalid instruction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>UndefVarError in Julia</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/julia/julia-undefinederror/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/julia/julia-undefinederror/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;UndefVarError&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when you try to use a variable or symbol that has not been defined in the current scope. This is a common error when variables are misspelled or used before assignment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typo in variable name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Variable used before assignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Variable defined in different scope (module, function)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing import of module or package&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check variable name spelling:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-julia" data-lang="julia"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;username &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(username) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# println(usename) # UndefVarError: usename not defined&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Initialize variables before use:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>